As of 2011, the Global Citizen group says it has recorded more than 19 million "actions" from its supporters, promoting a series of different targets.
It states that these actions helped world leaders announce commitments and policies corresponding to more than $37 billion, which are to affect the lives of over $2.25 billion people by 2030.
In early 2018, the group reported 390 commitments and announcements as a result of these actions, of which at least $10 billion has already been disbursed or raised.
The group estimates that secured funds have so far directly affected nearly 649 million people around the world.
